videos.headline: Buzzer-beater! Kyle Owens wins it for UC Riverside at the horn
videos.description: Kyle Owens grabs an offensive rebound and connects on a hook shot as the buzzer sounds to give UC Riverside a dramatic victory over Cal State Bakersfield.
